{"thag6.9:0.1":"Theragatha 6.9 ","thag6.9:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.9:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.9:0.4":"Purohitaputtajentattheragatha ","thag6.9:1.1":"“Jatimadena mattoham, ","thag6.9:1.2":"bhogaissariyena ca; ","thag6.9:1.3":"Santhanavannarupena, ","thag6.9:1.4":"madamatto acariham. ","thag6.9:2.1":"Nattano samakam kanci, ","thag6.9:2.2":"atirekam ca mannisam; ","thag6.9:2.3":"Atimanahato balo, ","thag6.9:2.4":"patthaddho ussitaddhajo. ","thag6.9:3.1":"Mataram pitarancapi, ","thag6.9:3.2":"annepi garusammate; ","thag6.9:3.3":"Na kanci abhivadesim, ","thag6.9:3.4":"manatthaddho anadaro. ","thag6.9:4.1":"Disva vinayakam aggam, ","thag6.9:4.2":"sarathinam varuttamam; ","thag6.9:4.3":"Tapantamiva adiccam, ","thag6.9:4.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","thag6.9:5.1":"Manam madanca chaddetva, ","thag6.9:5.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","thag6.9:5.3":"Sirasa abhivadesim, ","thag6.9:5.4":"sabbasattanamuttamam. ","thag6.9:6.1":"Atimano ca omano, ","thag6.9:6.2":"pahina susamuhata; ","thag6.9:6.3":"Asmimano samucchinno, ","thag6.9:6.4":"sabbe manavidha hata”ti. ","thag6.9:6.5":"… Jento purohitaputto thero …. "}